701700f-a.text:
Rhinelander Avenue, east from Barnes Avenue. In the center of the view, at Matthews Avenue, is a very old house, formerly on the B. Downing property. In the right background is Public school No. 83, at Bogart Avenue.
June 22, 1940
P.L. Sperr

701701f-a.text:
Rhinelander Avenue (left), south side, east from Barnes to Matthews Avenues. The corner house is number 1872 Barnes Avenue.
June 22, 1940
P.L. Sperr
